Job Description
We require a Business Manager for our firm who would be working with the senior management to cater the existing clientele and work on the leads to bring in more business. The candidate is supposed to work on the leads, do the coordination, attend meetings and conferences both locally and internationally.
Job Specification
The candidate should have previous experience of business development, sales and marketing who can work independently and must have extremely good communication skills.
